#
# This is the {{PRODUCT_NAME}} product repository.
# The {{PRODUCT_NAME}} instance is TRACKED here, other instances are ignored.
#
# ⚠️  IMPORTANT FOR SYNC:
#   - When running `sync-repos.sh pull`, this file may be overwritten by canonical
#   - The sync script automatically restores this product-specific version
#   - If sync fails to restore, manually regenerate from template:
#       sed 's/{{PRODUCT_NAME}}/{{PRODUCT_NAME}}/g' templates/product.gitignore.template > .gitignore
