# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# INSTANCES - Only {{PRODUCT_NAME}} instance is tracked
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# In product repos, we track OUR instance but ignore any other instances that
# might appear from sync operations or local testing.
_instances/*
!_instances/README.md
!_instances/{{PRODUCT_NAME}}
!_instances/{{PRODUCT_NAME}}/**

